{
  "stem": "9943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a lot of time was also spent to teach us these revolutionary songs and to, to march on the-- in May, May 1st marches, and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So it, it was a-- we, we needed really a lot of, of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a lot of work to put into really to be able to-- to get to, to start schooling in Poland.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I from-- that I was [INAUDIBLE] supposedly finishing the sixth class in, in Rostov, got into the fifth class of gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that gymnasium, we, we had an audition to other things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was Latin that one needed to know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then my parents, in Volodymyr-Volynskyi, they did open a, a store of, of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what-- things that you buy to make some frock-- well, dresses or, or, or [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] materials.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Textile--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they opened a, a store of textiles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not successful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't know how to make a-- to, to, to make a living, really, neither my father nor my mother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The house was sold, the one that we had in, in, in this Wlodzimierzec.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then gradually, this-- the money was spent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So pretty soon, my mother had to leave-- go back to Luck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she moved in with her parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father got a job in, in Brest-Litovsk, thanks to that cousin that was a cousin of the family that was also in Rostov.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came back to, to Brest, which was called Brzesc at that time because it was Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started to give lessons to support myself and remained in this Wlodzimierz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I finished at their gymnasium in 1929.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
